875
00:29:53,380 --> 00:29:54,740
[Ugh! We're doomed today.]

876
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:57,860
[Ha...]

877
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:57,590
Ugh, today...

878
00:29:57,900 --> 00:29:59,620
[Hahaha]

879
00:30:00,070 --> 00:30:01,600
Gosh, what a waste!

880
00:30:01,610 --> 00:30:02,530
No, it's OK.

881
00:30:03,780 --> 00:30:05,300
[It's OK. It's OK.]

882
00:30:05,990 --> 00:30:06,760
It's OK. It's OK.

883
00:30:06,100 --> 00:30:08,100
[It's... OK?]

884
00:30:08,430 --> 00:30:11,200
-It's OK that she spilled the kadayif? -It's OK.

885
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:13,260
[This is OK?]

886
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:13,160
Hey, she totally...

887
00:30:13,740 --> 00:30:16,740
[I'm breaking out in a cold sweat!]

888
00:30:18,510 --> 00:30:19,940
Sorry, Chef. -Don't be.

889
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:23,060
