894
00:30:27,100 --> 00:30:29,660
[Truffle Abalone Beef Patties PREP %]

895
00:30:27,620 --> 00:30:28,840
It's all cleaned.

896
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:30,870
It's 12 PM now.

897
00:30:30,300 --> 00:30:33,460
