901
00:30:35,910 --> 00:30:36,850
-Done. -OK.

902
00:30:37,140 --> 00:30:41,620
[Dubai chewy puffs:
Cut the rice cakes and puffs]

903
00:30:37,540 --> 00:30:39,740
Before cutting it, take it apart first,

904
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:41,490
and try to get 70 pieces.

905
00:30:41,520 --> 00:30:42,230
Cut like this...

906
00:30:42,060 --> 00:30:45,620
[Highlights of the upgraded Dubai chewy puffs]

907
00:30:43,630 --> 00:30:44,290
And then...

908
00:30:45,950 --> 00:30:47,610
