00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:48,820
[Use rice cakes instead of marshmallows!]

910
00:30:49,100 --> 00:30:51,980
[Cut these rice cakes into 70 pieces]

911
00:30:53,860 --> 00:30:57,580
[Cut into bite-sized pieces]

912
00:30:58,100 --> 00:31:01,180
[Enter the hell of cutting the rice cakes again]

913
00:31:02,260 --> 00:31:05,220
[70 pieces of rice cake—done!]

914
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:08,820
[Next: cutting the puffs]

915
00:31:05,750 --> 00:31:08,880
