-Cut like this?

916
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:14,180
[Cutting the puffs for the Dubai chewy puffs filling]

917
00:31:14,820 --> 00:31:17,940
[Younjung is cutting so many ingredients today]

918
00:31:18,180 --> 00:31:21,540
[Puffs stacking up layer by layer]

919
00:31:21,660 --> 00:31:24,020
[Twenty-eight... twenty-nine... thirty...]

920
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:26,220
[That's about 70 pieces!]

921
00:31:25,540 --> 00:31:26,230
OK.

922
00:31:26,380 --> 00:31:29,840
-This might not be enough. Set these aside for now. -Okay.

923
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:31,180
[Dubai chewy puffs] [Fry kadayif; Cut rice cakes & puffs; Portion the jam; Make cream]

924
00:31:30,030 --> 00:31:30,620
OK.

925
00:31:32,060 --> 00:31:35,420
[Time to season the ground beef for the beef patties]

926
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:34,080
Now, let's taste the sauce and check the seasoning.

927
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:35,430
Pour it in and stir it.

928
00:31:35,420 --> 00:31:37,620
[Dohoon joins in]
[Yoon Namno: Let me know when you're done seasoning.]

929
00:31:35,650 --> 00:31:37,920
Let me know when you're done seasoning.

930
00:31:37,970 --> 00:31:38,870
Just pour this in, right?

931
00:31:38,180 --> 00:31:40,660
[Working on his own tasks while lending support]

932
00:31:38,940 --> 00:31:40,340
Yes, pour it in and mix.

933
00:31:40,940 --> 00:31:44,140
[Pour in the sauce for the beef patties]

934
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,610
Give it a good mix.

935
00:31:43,680 --> 00:31:44,430
OK.

936
00:31:44,980 --> 00:31:48,900
[Focused]

937
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,400
It looks delicious.

938
00:31:53,500 --> 00:31:59,140
[Mixing the ground beef with all their strength]

939
00:31:59,420 --> 00:32:02,500
[Ah, this really gives your body a workout.]

940
00:32:04,460 --> 00:32:05,180
[Wow.]

941
00:32:06,980 --> 00:32:07,620
[Hyah!]

942
00:32:08,380 --> 00:32:11,020
[Back and forth]

943
00:32:11,580 --> 00:32:15,060
[Forearm muscle usage: 100%]

944
00:32:15,620 --> 00:32:18,820
[The perfect beef patty duo]

945
00:32:19,820 --> 00:32:21,300
[Come on, here's the frying pan.]

946
00:32:21,300 --> 00:32:24,100
[Yoon Namno: I'll just taste it. Let's shape a small one and fry it.]

947
00:32:24,100 --> 00:32:26,020
[Yoon Namno: Then we'll decide if it needs more seasoning.]

948
00:32:26,340 --> 00:32:27,540
[Shape a small piece first, then.]

949
00:32:27,540 --> 00:32:29,220
[Doesn't need to be too big, right?]

950
00:32:27,750 --> 00:32:29,940
-Doesn't need to be too big, right? -Just fry a small piece.

951
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:31,780
[But not too small, or I won't be able to tell
if the seasoning is right.]

952
00:32:31,420 --> 00:32:32,340
-Ah. -Got it.

953
00:32:33,340 --> 00:32:35,180
[Ah, let's just go with the original size. Haha...]

954
00:32:35,320 --> 00:32:36,500
-Chef. -Yes.

955
00:32:35,380 --> 00:32:37,620
[Kim Dohoon: Chef, it's hard for me to do it
because I'm wearing gloves.]

956
00:32:37,620 --> 00:32:38,980
