1721
00:57:12,940 --> 00:57:13,820
[Park Myungsoo: Fold it 5 times.]

1722
00:57:14,050 --> 00:57:15,220
Yes, like this.

1723
00:57:15,220 --> 00:57:15,770
OK.

1724
00:57:15,770 --> 00:57:16,540
