1751
00:58:02,060 --> 00:58:03,980
[Looks like he's feeling lonely…]

1752
00:58:04,540 --> 00:58:07,420
[Lingering]
[Looks like he misses human touch.]

1753
00:58:07,780 --> 00:58:09,740
[Yoon Namno: We need
to finish this quickly now.]

1754
00:58:09,030 --> 00:58:09,760
Got it.

1755
00:58:09,980 --> 00:58:12,700
[Hong Jinkyung: I'll do it fast.
