1801
00:59:50,860 --> 00:59:53,220
[Hahaha]

1802
00:59:51,270 --> 00:59:52,520
I'm so tired.

1803
00:59:53,420 --> 00:59:54,860
[Ooh, I'm drenched in sweat.]

1804
00:59:55,100 --> 00:59:57,220
