1824
01:00:33,900 --> 01:00:36,260
[My parents are ugly, okay?]

1825
01:00:36,850 --> 01:00:37,970
Okay.

1826
01:00:36,940 --> 01:00:38,620
[Okay.]

1827
01:00:38,940 --> 01:00:40,820
[Then Jinkyung, are your parents good-looking?]

1828
01:00:42,020 --> 01:00:43,500
[Not really.]

1829
01:00:46,940 --> 01:00:49,140
[Can't even complain about that...]

1830
01:00:48,450 --> 01:00:49,480
Sprinkle some more flour.

1831
01:00:49,480 --> 01:00:50,220
Okay.

1832
01:00:49,940 --> 01:00:50,940
[Sprinkling some flour.]

1833
