1857
01:01:28,700 --> 01:01:29,740
[Dohoon.]

1858
01:01:28,800 --> 01:01:29,860
-Dohoon. -Here.

1859
01:01:29,860 --> 01:01:31,720
-Dohoon. -Here.

1860
01:01:30,140 --> 01:01:31,580
[Nervous]

1861
01:01:31,740 --> 01:01:34,140
[You're tired, right?]

1862
01:01:32,990 --> 01:01:34,440
Noona.

1863
01:01:34,440 --> 01:01:35,910
