1873
01:01:51,380 --> 01:01:52,290
He did.

1874
01:01:52,140 --> 01:01:54,060
[Yoon Namno: Hyung,
his fan count is 10 times yours.]

1875
01:01:54,340 --> 01:01:55,940
[Hong Jinkyung: He's truly
a man with nothing left to lose.]

1876
01:01:56,020 --> 01:01:58,340
[Jung Hae-in's future is bright,
