1907
01:02:43,780 --> 01:02:46,020
[Roll it out wide and large.]

1908
01:02:46,140 --> 01:02:49,380
-Push it all the way with your hands. -Okay.

1909
01:02:46,860 --> 01:02:49,380
[Push it all the way.]

1910
01:02:49,380 --> 01:02:51,190
Keep rolling.

1911
01:02:50,460 --> 01:02:53,340
[Da!] [Unusual skill]

1912
