[Dough-rolling Master—Park Myungsoo]

1923
01:03:09,180 --> 01:03:11,960
I feel like I've seen someone like this
in a Jajangmyeon shop.

1924
01:03:11,960 --> 01:03:12,900
It's too thin.

1925
01:03:12,900 --> 01:03:14,370
