1926
01:03:14,370 --> 01:03:15,550
It needs to be about this thick.

1927
01:03:15,020 --> 01:03:18,420
[A master sharing his secrets]

1928
01:03:15,550 --> 01:03:16,960
-About this thick. -Yeah, okay.

1929
01:03:16,960 --> 01:03:18,550
-About this thick. -Exactly.

1930
01:03:18,550 --> 01:03:20,630
-I'll do it. -You do it.

1931
01:03:19,780 --> 01:03:22,100
[Another newcomer appears]

1932
01:03:22,190 --> 01:03:25,560
Push it all the way. Push it like this.

1933
01:03:23,700 --> 01:03:26,460
[Harsh coaching from the master]

1934
01:03:25,560 --> 01:03:26,790
Like this.

1935
01:03:26,900 --> 01:03:28,340
[Don't be so protective of your body!]

1936
