1952
01:04:04,300 --> 01:04:05,070
-The drumstick part. -Okay.

1953
01:04:04,900 --> 01:04:06,980
[Yoon Namno: It really hurts if you get poked.]

1954
01:04:05,070 --> 01:04:07,010
-It really hurts if you get poked. -Okay.

1955
01:04:07,010 --> 01:04:09,100
-There can't be a single bone left. -I'll do it carefully.

1956
01:04:07,460 --> 01:04:09,100
[Meticulous]
[I'll do it carefully!]

1957
01:04:09,670 --> 01:04:11,810
-There can't be any bones. Not a single one. -Okay.

1958
01:04:09,860 --> 01:04:11,940
[Repeatedly warning]
[Yoon Namno: There can't be any bones.
