1960
01:04:17,140 --> 01:04:19,580
[Chef, no cartilage either, right?]

1961
01:04:18,750 --> 01:04:19,750
No cartilage either.

1962
01:04:19,660 --> 01:04:22,780
[Chef, I don't need to shred the chicken breast
