1963
01:04:19,750 --> 01:04:21,040
-Chef. -Here.

1964
01:04:21,040 --> 01:04:23,930
I don't need to shred the chicken breast
into tiny bits, right? Should I?

1965
01:04:23,930 --> 01:04:24,560
Shred it.

1966
01:04:24,560 --> 01:04:25,540
-I mean... -Okay.

1967
